prompts.frontCover:
A humorous and beautifully rendered watercolor illustration of Lao Lao as the star of her own cooking show. She is depicted as a cartoon/illustrated character, highly resembling her reference photo, including her exact hairstyle, facial features, body proportions, and her purple and white floral patterned shirt. She stands behind a kitchen counter, joyfully and perhaps a little chaotically, tossing a stir-fry in a large wok with exaggerated flair, sending illustrated vegetables flying playfully in the air around her. Jordan, also as a cartoon/illustrated character highly resembling his reference photo (including hairstyle, facial features, proportions, and his gray t-shirt), stands beside her with a big, amused smile, holding an empty bowl and chopsticks, eagerly waiting for a taste. The entire scene is captured in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to the World's Best Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
